data.description: This exceptional investment opportunity includes numerous Airbnb rentals already booked and prepared for seamless transition to your future buyer. Enjoy water views from every window and be captivated by the mesmerizing sunsets. This exquisite 3-bedroom residence is ideally situated on a picturesque street, offering spectacular sunset vistas, and just a short distance from the beach. Inside, an open-concept living and dining area creates the perfect space for hosting gatherings, with a spacious kitchen that provides stunning views. The primary bedroom is generously sized and boasts a luxurious, spa-like ensuite bathroom. Great for short-term rentals, or gathering with family and friends.     The Indian Beach Subdivision offers access to a private fishing pier, a pool, and tennis courts, making it one of Galveston's premier West End communities. Don't miss the unique opportunity to own a property so close to both the bay and the beach. Contact us today to schedule your private viewing.
